Sentencas: Honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-delta (LSCF-GDC) composite cathodes are prepared using the breath figures (BFs) method with nontoxic and easily available water droplets as templates.
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fabrication of honeycomb porous membranes is realized in a relatively humid environment, using a volatile solvent.
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microstructure and morphology of the membranes produced are investigated by scanning electron microscopy (SEM).
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SEM micrographs suggest that experimental conditions, such as ambient temperature, relative humidity, and concentration of polymer and LSCF-GDC powder, which have direct influence on the solvent evaporation affects the pore structure of the porous membranes.
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) is used to evaluate the polarization resistance of LSCF-GDC composite cathodes prepared at different experimental conditions.
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The honeycomb porous LSCF-GDC composite cathode showing average pore diameter of 10 mu m illustrates the lowest polarization resistance.
Titulo: Preparation of honeycomb porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ composite cathodes by breath figures method for solid oxide fuel cells
